Project Name

Multi-Story Steel Frame Seismic Retrofit Using X-Bracing Optimization

Domain
Task Type: Structures
Domain: seismic_retrofit
Problem Statement

A four-story steel moment-resisting frame has inadequate lateral stiffness under seismic loading.

The model must determine the optimal placement of steel X-braces to improve seismic performance while minimizing additional steel weight.

The model should produce a JSON file containing:

Floors selected for retrofit
Bay locations
Brace section sizes
Estimated total steel weight
Expected maximum interstory drift ratio
Public Files (data/)
building_geometry.json
story_properties.json
load_combinations.json
steel_sections.json
design_limits.json
output_schema.json
These files include:

Frame geometry
Story heights
Bay spacing
Dead and live loads
Material properties
Available steel sections
Drift limits
Weight calculation formulas
